column5: Has anyone traveled HWY 129 between Thessalon and Foleyet? Just wondering if the 60 miles we are going to save by going that way instead of 17 to 101 will be worth it? Thanks.

Traveled the first 80 miles fom thessalon to Aubrey Falls last week. Good condition, little traffic, Beautiful scenery of the Missisaugi(sp) river valley. Also saw 2 black bears. I enjoyed the trip and motored right along about 65 miles per hour. Good luck Eric
Thanks Eric....We are planning a trip right now and that helps out immensely. Good news.
